ŃI know a place called Vickers, a colossal
factory that makes guns, cars, planes and
sewing machines.

I know a place called vickers that has guns
in rows, like soldiers lining up for battle.

I know a factory called Vickers, where ideas
become into inventions.

By Francesca, Mayplace Primary School

